This Privacy Policy is
intended to inform you about the types of information we collect and do not
collect when you use our Service, as well as our commitment to protecting any
data we might access.

## No Personal Data Collection

Our Service is designed in a way that we do not collect, store, or process any
personal data from our users.

### Data We Do Not Collect

We do not collect any information that can be used to personally identify you,
such as:

  * Names
  * Email addresses
  * Physical addresses
  * Phone numbers
  * IP addresses
  * Any other form of personal or sensitive information

## Usage Data

While we do not collect personal data, we may collect non-personally
identifiable information related to the usage of our Service.

This includes:

  * Type of API requests made
  * Frequency of API calls
  * General usage statistics

This data is purely for the purpose of improving the Service and analyzing
usage trends.
